  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 09c0819852a80204586d7f9de68fa6d1, type: 3}
  m_Name: Starter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalSO
  title: Turn Back
  entry: I miss my wife. The catacombs are scary, I lost my friends- and soon my
    life. I fear that my speech is fading day by day. My heart has gone cold no hope
    left to hold. I lost my hearing. That monster- please I pray for the men and
    women who stand along my soon corpse.  An end of your own volition is better
    fit than what these entities hold in store.
  number: 2
  image: {fileID: 0}
  playerResponse: LOL anyplace is better than being around her.
